Material Request :

üß© TAB 1 ‚Äì Details

| Field                | Simple Meaning                                                                                             |
| -------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Series**           | Auto ID format of this document (like MAT-MR-YYYY-0001).                                                   |
| **Transaction Date** | Date when you create the material request.                                                                 |
| **Purpose**          | Why you need this request ‚Üí e.g. *Purchase*, *Material Transfer*, *Manufacture*, *Customer Provided*, etc. |
| **Required By**      | The date by which you want items to be available.                                                          |
| **Price List**       | Default buying price list used to fetch item rates.                                                        |


üß± Items Section

| Field                | Meaning                                                   |
| -------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Scan Barcode**     | Scan item barcode (if enabled) ‚Äî auto fills item details. |
| **Item Code**        | Item you are requesting.                                  |
| **Required By**      | When this item is needed (can be different per item).     |
| **Quantity**         | How many units you need.                                  |
| **Target Warehouse** | Where you want these items to go after procurement.       |
| **UOM**              | Unit of Measure (e.g., Nos, Kg, Box).                     |


üß© TAB 2 ‚Äì Terms

| Field                            | Simple Meaning                                                                                       |
| -------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Terms**                        | You can select predefined ‚ÄúTerms & Conditions‚Äù.                                                      |
| **Terms and Conditions Content** | Editable area where you can type or modify any terms (like payment terms, delivery, warranty, etc.). |


üß© TAB 3 ‚Äì More Info

| Section              | Fields                             | Simple Meaning                                                                                                |
| -------------------- | ---------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Printing Details** | **Letter Head**, **Print Heading** | Choose which letterhead to use for print (like company logo header), and custom heading for print (optional). |


‚öôÔ∏è Button: Get Items From
- This button helps you auto-fetch items from other sources instead of manually typing them.

| Option                      | Meaning                                                                          |
| --------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Bill of Materials (BOM)** | Fetch items required for manufacturing a product.                                |
| **Sales Order**             | Fetch items from a customer‚Äôs sales order (for subcontracting or make-to-order). |
| **Product Bundle**          | Fetch items grouped under a single product bundle (kit).                         |


