üí∏ Additional Discount & Totals

| Field                              | Meaning                                             |
| ---------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------- |
| **Apply Additional Discount On**   | Choose base for discount (Net Total / Grand Total). |
| **Additional Discount % / Amount** | Final overall discount on total bill.               |
| **Grand Total (INR)**              | Final amount before rounding.                       |
| **Rounding Adjustment (INR)**      | Small +/‚Äì difference while rounding.                |
| **Rounded Total (INR)**            | Final rounded amount to pay.                        |
| **Disable Rounded Total**          | Stops auto-rounding (keeps decimal).                |
