here,
Apply Putaway Rule :
If checked ‚úÖ, ERPNext will automatically decide where to store items inside a warehouse based on Putaway Rules.

What is a Putaway Rule?
- A Putaway Rule tells ERPNext where (in which bin, rack, or warehouse section) to place an item when it arrives.
- Think of it as a ‚Äústorage placement guide‚Äù for your items.



