| ------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Enabled**                          | Tick this to **activate** the price list. Disabled lists can‚Äôt be used.               |
| **Price List Name**                  | The **name of your price list**, e.g., ‚ÄúStandard Buying‚Äù or ‚ÄúRetail Selling.‚Äù         |
| **Currency**                         | The **currency** in which prices are defined, e.g., INR, USD.                         |
| **Buying**                           | Tick if this list is for **purchase prices** (used in Purchase Orders, etc.).         |
| **Selling**                          | Tick if this list is for **sales prices** (used in Sales Orders, etc.).               |
| **Price Not UOM Dependent**          | If ticked, price stays **same for all UOMs** (Unit of Measures).                      |
| **Applicable for Countries (Table)** | Add countries where this price list is valid. Useful for **multi-country companies**. |


