Pricing Rule

| **Section / Field**                 | **Simple Meaning (Easy to Remember)**                                          |
| ----------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **Naming Series**                   | Auto name pattern for rule (e.g., PRLE-0001).                                  |
| **Title**                           | Rule name ‚Äî describe offer or condition (e.g., ‚Äú10% Discount on Electronics‚Äù). |
| **Disable**                         | Tick to **turn off** the rule temporarily.                                     |
| **Apply On**                        | What rule applies to ‚Äî e.g., Item, Item Group, Brand, Customer Group, etc.     |
| **Apply Rule On Item Code (Table)** | Select item(s) for which the rule will apply.                                  |
| **Price or Product Discount**       | Choose **Price** (reduce rate) or **Discount** (apply % off).                  |
| **Warehouse**                       | If rule applies only to items in a specific warehouse.                         |
| **Mixed Conditions**                | Apply rule if **multiple conditions** match together.                          |
| **Is Cumulative**                   | Allows **multiple rules to apply together**.                                   |
| **Coupon Code Based**               | Rule is applied **only when coupon code is entered**.                          |


üõí Discount on Other Item

| Field                   | Meaning                                                                                         |
| ----------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Apply Rule On Other** | Apply discount on a different item when buying another (e.g., ‚ÄúBuy Laptop, get Mouse 50% off‚Äù). |


üë• Party Information

| Field                | Meaning                                                                |
| -------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Selling / Buying** | Select whether rule applies in **sales** or **purchase** transactions. |


