supplier

üîπ 1. Details Tab

| **Field**                        | **Simple Meaning (Easy to Remember)**                                |
| -------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Supplier Name**                | Supplier‚Äôs full name or company name.                                |
| **Supplier Group**               | Category of supplier (e.g., Local, Overseas, Raw Material).          |
| **Country**                      | Supplier‚Äôs country.                                                  |
| **Supplier Type**                | Defines if the supplier is an **Individual or Company**.             |
| **Is Transporter**               | Tick if the supplier provides **transportation/logistics** services. |
| **Billing Currency**             | Default currency for transactions with this supplier.                |
| **Price List**                   | Default **Buying Price List** used in Purchase transactions.         |
| **Default Company Bank Account** | Your company‚Äôs default bank account for paying this supplier.        |
| **Is Internal Supplier**         | Tick if this supplier is another **branch of your company**.         |
| **Supplier Details**             | Additional information like description or notes.                    |
| **Website / Print Language**     | Supplier‚Äôs website and preferred print language.                     |


