| **GST Category**              | Registration type (e.g., Registered, Unregistered, SEZ). |
| **Tax Category**              | Custom tax group applicable.                             |
| **Reverse Charge Applicable** | Tick if you need to pay GST instead of supplier.         |
| **PAN / Tax ID**              | Supplier‚Äôs PAN or international tax ID.                  |
| **Tax Withholding Category**  | TDS category if applicable.                              |


