üîπ 5. Settings Tab

| **Field**                                                    | **Meaning**                                                       |
| ------------------------------------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Allow Purchase Invoice Creation Without Purchase Order**   | Allows direct Purchase Invoice without a PO.                      |
| **Allow Purchase Invoice Creation Without Purchase Receipt** | Allows direct Purchase Invoice without PR.                        |
| **Is Frozen**                                                | Prevents any new transactions for this supplier.                  |
| **Disabled**                                                 | Completely deactivate the supplier.                               |
| **Block Supplier**                                           | Stop further orders/invoices ‚Äî used when supplier is blacklisted. |


